name: Sweet to be Minted by Dada Dot Dot

metadata.name: Polo Mint #1/23
metadata.description: This is an edition of 1 unique NFT. It relates to the image of a Polo mint, in this case the first in the packet. This in turn forms part of a series of 23 NFTs. There is one NFT for each of the doughnut shaped sweets found in this particular roll (packet). Purchase of the NFT is accompanied, via unlockable content found at dadadotdot.com, by a digital download of the original RAW file image, out-takes from the series, a copy of the Dada Dot Dot Artist Manifesto and “physical residue” that posts free-of-charge globally. In addition, audio access to the artist is granted via a private patrons-only channel on Discord.
metadata.Hidden Property: The original RAW file image, out-takes from the series and “physical residue” is available to the first owner by connecting their wallet to the artist's website.
